  "text": "Huang et al. [CITATION_1] develop a e-business model for the food souvenir industry in Taiwan, inspired by the e-commerce business model. The focus of their innovation is value creation. According to their model, the final customers are able to order online, and local providers are responsible for the supply and delivery of orders.",
